Refund Policy
Custom Orders

We keep custom orders on record for 7 days so therefore we can check the date of completion, and help you get your money’s worth



Within 1-3 Days

If you request a refund within 1-3 days of your order you have 2 options, redo the logo, or refund your money.



Within 4-7 Days

If you request a refund within 4-7 days of your order, You can get a Refund



7-10 Days

If your order is over 7 days old, and still on record, you can receive half of a full refund



Release’s Refunds
Pantherz Development Does Not allow refunds on releases, this is because once a release has been purchased you have access to a download link, therefore you have the full possibility to redownload our resources.



Free Resources/Free discounts/Limited Time Free discounts Are not Covered by our refund policy
